    • Method Detail

      • unCompressCacheItem

        public void unCompressCacheItem()
                         throws java.lang.Exception
        This method overwrite the super class - EcogridCompressedDataCacheItem. It specifys the gunzip method to uncompress the file. The new ungzip file will be the the cacheitem file name without the file extension. An file location will be the cachedata/unzip/cacheitemname/ If this is tar file too, we will untar it after ungzip it.
        Specified by:
        unCompressCacheItem in class EcogridCompressedDataCacheItem
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
